@startuml
title Admin Food Management Flow
actor Admin
participant Frontend
participant Backend
database DB

Admin -> Frontend: Login
Frontend -> Backend: POST /api/users/login
Backend -> DB: Verify credentials
Backend --> Frontend: Return userId

Admin -> Frontend: Create Food (userId in payload)
Frontend -> Backend: POST /api/foods
Backend -> DB: Verify user is Admin
Backend -> DB: Create food
Backend --> Frontend: 200 OK

Admin -> Frontend: Update price / availability
Frontend -> Backend: PATCH /api/foods/{id}
Backend -> DB: Verify Admin role, Update fields
Backend --> Frontend: 200 OK
@enduml
